#: widgets/KoTagFilterWidget.cpp:39
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"<qt>Entering search terms here will add to, or remove resources from the "
"current tag view.<para>To filter based on the partial, case insensitive name "
"of a resource:<br><icode>partialname</icode> or <icode>!partialname</icode>."
"</para><para>In-/exclusion of other tag sets:<br><icode>[Tagname]</icode> or "
"<icode>![Tagname]</icode>.</para><para>Case sensitive and full name matching "
"in-/exclusion:<br><icode>\"ExactMatch\"</icode> or <icode>!\"ExactMatch\"</"
"icode>.</para>Filter results cannot be saved for the <interface>All Presets</"
"interface> view.<br>In this view, pressing <interface>Enter</interface> or "
"clearing the filter box will restore all items.<br>Create and/or switch to a "
"different tag if you want to save filtered resources into named sets.</qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt>Má chuireann tú téarmaí cuardaigh isteach anseo, cuirfear acmhainní leis "
"an radharc clibeanna reatha nó bainfear iad den radharc.<para>Chun scagadh a "
"dhéanamh bunaithe ar ainm acmhainne atá páirteach agus neamhíogair ó thaobh "
"cás de:<br><icode>partialname</icode> nó <icode>!partialname</icode>.</"
"para><para>Tacair clibeanna eile a chur isteach/a eisiamh:<br><icode>[Ainm "
"Clibeanna]</icode> nó <icode>![Ainm Clibeanna]</icode>.</"
"para><para>Meaitseáil ainm iomlán agus íogair ó thaobh cás de:<br><icode>"
"\"ExactMatch\"</icode> nó <icode>!\"ExactMatch\"</icode>.</para>Ní féidir "
"torthaí scagaire a shábháil don radharc <interface>Gach Réamhshocrú</"
"interface>.<br>Sa radharc seo, má bhrúnn tú <interface>Iontráil</interface> "
"nó má ghlanann tú an bosca scagaire, cuirfear na míreanna go léir ar ais."
"<br>Cruthaigh agus/nó aistrigh chuig clib dhifriúil más mian leat acmhainní "
"scagtha a shábháil i dtacair ainmnithe.</qt>"

#: widgets/KoTagFilterWidget.cpp:52
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"<qt>Entering search terms here will add to, or remove resources from the "
"current tag view.<para>To filter based on the partial, case insensitive name "
"of a resource:<br><icode>partialname</icode> or <icode>!partialname</icode>."
"</para><para>In-/exclusion of other tag sets:<br><icode>[Tagname]</icode> or "
"<icode>![Tagname]</icode>.</para><para>Case sensitive and full name matching "
"in-/exclusion:<br><icode>\"ExactMatch\"</icode> or <icode>!\"ExactMatch\"</"
"icode>.</para>Pressing <interface>Enter</interface> or clicking the "
"<interface>Save</interface> button will save the changes.</qt>"
msgstr ""
"<qt>Má chuireann tú téarmaí cuardaigh isteach anseo, cuirfear acmhainní leis "
"an radharc clibeanna reatha nó bainfear iad den radharc.<para>Chun scagadh a "
"dhéanamh bunaithe ar ainm acmhainne atá páirteach agus neamhíogair ó thaobh "
"cás de:<br><icode>partialname</icode> nó <icode>!partialname</icode>.</"
"para><para>Isteach/eisiamh tacair clibeanna eile:<br><icode>[Ainm "
"Clibeanna]</icode> nó <icode>![Ainm Clibeanna]</icode>.</"
"para><para>Meaitseáil ainm iomlán agus íogair ó thaobh cás de:<br><icode>"
"\"ExactMatch\"</icode> nó <icode>!\"ExactMatch\"</icode>.</para>Má bhrúnn tú "
"<interface>Iontráil</interface> nó má chliceálann tú ar an gcnaipe "
"<interface>Sábháil</interface>, sábhálfar na hathruithe.</qt>"

